          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p dir="ltr">Amazon's <a href="https://www.amazon.com/blackfriday?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Black Friday 2024 sale</a> kicks off November 21 and runs through November 29. As usual, thousands of items across the entire site will be discounted once the week-long event is live, but there are already a bunch of early deals to take advantage of, including price cuts to numerous Amazon devices like Amazon Fire tablets, TVs, soundbars, and more.</p><p dir="ltr">If you're looking for a simple cloud gaming setup, you can <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DGGHMK89?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">grab a bundle</a> that includes an Amazon Fire TV Stick 4K, an Xbox Wireless controller, and a one-month Game Pass Ultimate prepaid subscription card for $75 (was $137). That's barely more than what a first-party Xbox controller normally costs by itself, and the whole setup will let you stream games over the cloud via Game Pass, including many of the latest Xbox Series X games like Halo Infinite, Starfield, Call of Duty: Black Ops 6, and the upcoming Indiana Jones and the Great Circle when it launches on December 6. Check out a list of more early Black Friday deals on Amazon devices below.</p><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4399492-bundle.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4399492" data-ratio="0.552" data-width="1000" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4399492-bundle.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4399492"></a><figcaption>Amazon Fire TV Stick 4K, Xbox Wireless Controller, 1-Month Game Pass Ultimate card</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4399492-bundle.jpg"></figure><h2 dir="ltr">Early Black Friday Amazon Device Deals</h2><ul><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DGGHMK89?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Fire Stick 4K + Xbox Controller + 1-Month Game Pass Ultimate</a> -- $75 (<del>$137</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DGGG4NNK?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Fire TV Stick 4K Max + Xbox Controller + 1-Month Game Pass Ultimate</a> -- $80 (<del>$147</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/introducing-amazon-fire-tv-43-inch-omni-qled-series-smart-tv/dp/B09N6LRBTR?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">43-inch Amazon Fire TV Omni QLED 4K TV</a> -- $370 (<del>$450</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/amazon-fire-tv-50-inch-omni-series-4k-smart-tv/dp/B08T6F8YBH?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">50-inch Amazon Fire TV Omni Series 4K Smart TV</a> -- $330 (<del>$480</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/amazon-fire-tv-55-inch-4-series-4k-smart-tv/dp/B0B3H6JPYZ?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">55-Inch Amazon Fire TV 4-Series 4K TV</a> -- $340 (<del>$520</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/eero-reliable-gigabit-connect-Coverage/dp/B08ZK39NSL?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon eero 6+ Mesh Wifi Router</a> -- $100 (<del>$140</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Amazon-powerful-display-octa-core-processor/dp/B0B1VQ1ZQY?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon Fire Max 11 tablet</a> -- $140 (<del>$230</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Amazon_Fire_HD_10/dp/B0BL5PYD69?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon Fire HD 10 Tablet - 64GB</a> -- $85 (<del>$180</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Amazon_Fire_HD_10_Kids_Pro/dp/B0BL6DCNGR?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon Fire HD 10 Kids Pro</a> -- $110 (<del>$190</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Introducing-Amazon-Soundbar-speaker-Virtual/dp/B0C4BZ28PG?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon Fire TV Soundbar 2.0</a> --</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/all-new-amazon-fire-tv-stick-4k-max/dp/B0BP9SNVH9?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon Fire TV Stick 4K Max</a> -- $33 (<del>$60</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Blink-Outdoor-4th-Gen-3-Camera/dp/B0B1N5FK48?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Blink Outdoor 4</a> -- $48 (<del>$110</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Echo-Spot-Globe-Electric-Smart/dp/B0DGRP3C5L?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Echo Spot with Globe electric Smart Bulb bundle</a> -- $80 (<del>$92</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/All-new-Ring-Battery-Doorbell-Indoor/dp/B0D9344TXC?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Ring Doorbell with Indoor Cam (2nd Gen)</a> -- $80 (<del>$140</del>)</li></ul><hr><p dir="ltr">Beyond Amazon's own hardware, there are some other notable early Black Friday deals available now, including a slight discount that drops <a href="https://www.amazon.com/PlayStation-Store-Gift-Card-Digital/dp/B07C438TMN?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">$25 digital PlayStation Store cards</a> down to $22.50, price cuts to PC hardware like the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Logitech-Lightspeed-PowerPlay-Compatible-Lightsync/dp/B07L4BM851?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Logitech G502 Lightspeed wireless gaming mouse</a>, and other electronics like <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/early-black-friday-apple-deal-airtag-4-pack-for-70-restocked-at-amazon/1100-6516754/" data-ref-id="1100-6516754">Apple's AirTags</a> You'll also find deals on <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/one-of-the-best-lego-minecraft-sets-drops-to-best-price-yet-at-amazon/1100-6527684/" data-ref-id="1100-6527684">Lego sets</a>, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Funko-Pop-Advent-Calendar-Holiday/dp/B09Q94B9Q8?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Funko Pops</a>, and more. You can also add to your bookshelf for cheap with <a href="https://www.amazon.com/promotion/psp/A1TTCJG2VRP8H4?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20&amp;ref=psp_pc_cart_collapse" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon's Buy Two, Get One Free Book Sale</a>. You can browse <a href="https://www.amazon.com/blackfriday?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">all the early Black Friday discounts on Amazon's website</a>.</p><p dir="ltr">Amazon's Black Friday sale is technically only a week-long, but the savings won't end there. The event will be immediately followed up by <strong>Amazon's Cyber Monday sale</strong>, which runs from <strong>November 29 through December 2</strong> and will likely bring a whole new crop of deals--though we expect some of the Black Friday discounts will make an encore appearance. Be sure to keep an eye on <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/deals/">GameSpot's deals coverage</a> for more Black Friday discounts from Amazon, Best Buy, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/walmart-black-friday-best-gaming-tech-toy-deals/2900-5942/" data-ref-id="2900-5942">Walmart</a>, and more.</p><hr><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/get-dark-souls-board-game-for-only-51-and-roleplaying-sourcebook-for-30/1100-6527696/">Get Dark Souls Board Game For Only $51 And Roleplaying Sourcebook For $30</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/ps5-pro-disc-drive-is-sold-out-at-most-retailers-but-walmart-has-it-for-now/1100-6526391/">PS5 Pro Disc Drive Is Sold Out At Most Retailers, But Walmart Has It (For Now)</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/ps5-pro-preorders-live-at-amazon-walmart-and-best-buy/1100-6526406/">The PS5 Pro Is Available Now And Eligible For One-Day Delivery At Amazon</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (5)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-legend-of-zelda-echoes-of-wisdom-is-on-sale-for-a-great-price/1100-6527148/">Zelda: Echoes Of Wisdom Is Already On Sale For 25% Off</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/dragon-age-the-veilguard-collectors-edition-preorders-available-ahead-of-this-weeks-launch/1100-6525830/">Dragon Age: The Veilguard Collector's Edition In Stock On Launch Day For PS5 And Xbox</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/special-edition-lord-of-the-rings-trilogy-4k-gift-set-releases-this-holiday-preorders-live-at-amazon/1100-6527414/">Lord Of The Rings 4K Gift Set Releases This Holiday, Comes With One Ring Collectible</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/build-shadow-the-hedgehogs-head-out-of-720-lego-bricks-for-only-56/1100-6525229/">Target's Exclusive Shadow The Hedgehog Lego Set Is Discounted Just Weeks After Its Release</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/king-boos-haunted-mansion-lego-mario-set-gets-first-price-cut-at-amazon/1100-6525381/">King Boo's Haunted Mansion Lego Mario Set Gets First Price Cut At Amazon</a></li>   </ul> </div>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
